Much depends on how children are raised to think about their role in the family. I hope Raelene does not pass along her parents attitudes to her children. Boys who are raised to do housework are much more likely to become men who see housework as part of what they do.  Even so, our society still tells men that their job is to HELP with housework not to DO housework.<br>

